::DeathScythe/Ramulus::

DeathScythe frowns, stopping in the air. His scanners had lost their lock on 
the new bot. He looks around, looking down at a clearing. The assassin shakes 
his head. She wouldn't be that stupid...

He makes a spiral, his scanners on the search.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
His scanners reporting SnowCat entering the clearing, Ramulus speeds up, also 
heading for it.
